OL,3,CWest Midlands Mayor set to take over
OL,4,CPolice and Crime Commissioner powers
OL,6,FThe West Midlands Mayor will take over
OL,7,Fthe powers of the Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner (PCC) after a decision by
OL,9,Fthe Home Secretary.
OL,11,FIn a statement on X, posted on
OL,12,FWednesday 6 December, Andy Street said
OL,13,Fthe new Home Secretary, James
OL,14,FCleverley, had agreed to transfer
OL,15,Fpowers from the current PCC, Simon
OL,16,FFoster, to himself.
OL,18,FHe added: "Crime has doubled in 8
OL,19,Fyears and our force is now in special
OL,20,Fmeasures. We cannot go on like this.
